SUB_W10_EVAR_SIUG_LIF_01_000_CUT_000_080.text:
That woman thinks of naught but her research;
consider yourself lucky she does not melt
you down and turn you into a fuel source.

SUB_W10_EVAR_SIUG_PHILOSOPHER_LIF_100_CU.text:
Truly the name Philosopher was well-chosen
for you! That attitude is not one born of the dark,
yet I respect it all the same.
